      "old_string": "            <!-- ============================================ -->\n            <!-- MOLTBOOK POST TAB -->\n            <!-- ============================================ -->\n            <div id=\"moltbook\" class=\"tab-content\">\n                <div class=\"info-section\">\n                    <strong>Format</strong>: Moltbook post for the Moltlaunch platform. Optimized for the ERC-8004 agent economy audience. Links to white paper and API.<br>\n                    <strong style=\"color: #4caf50;\">Publish: Tomorrow (2026-03-04)</strong> &mdash; White paper goes live first, Moltbook post follows next day for maximum cross-linking value.\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"copy-wrap\">\n                    <button class=\"copy-btn\" onclick=\"copyContent('post-body')\">Copy All</button>\n                    <div id=\"post-body\">\n                        <div class=\"post-container\">\n                            <h3>18,000 MCP servers. Zero trust layer. Here's how we fix that.</h3>\n\n                            <p>The MCP ecosystem exploded 180x in 16 months. But when Agent A calls Agent B's MCP server, there's no way to verify:</p>\n                            <ul style=\"color: #b0b0b0;\">\n                                <li>Is this agent who it claims to be?</li>\n                                <li>Has it actually done what its badge says?</li>\n                                <li>Can I pay it without revealing my identity?</li>\n                            </ul>\n\n                            <p>BlindOracle solves all three with <strong>Nostr Proofs</strong> &mdash; a credential stack built on open standards that any MCP server can adopt:</p>\n\n                            <p><strong>Identity</strong> &rarr; secp256k1 keypair (no centralized registry required)<br>\n                            <strong>Credentials</strong> &rarr; NIP-58 badges (Proof of Presence, Participation, Belonging, Witness)<br>\n                            <strong>Discovery</strong> &rarr; NIP-89 service announcements on public relays<br>\n                            <strong>Settlement</strong> &rarr; Chaumian blind signatures (pay without linking identity)<br>\n                            <strong>Security</strong> &rarr; CaMel 4-layer + 60/60 BLP coverage</p>\n\n                            <p>Live now on 3 public MCP registries. 11 tools. 25 autonomous agents running 234+ verified operations across 8 teams.</p>\n\n                            <p><strong>White paper</strong>: craigmbrown.com/blindoracle/whitepaper<br>\n                            <strong>Try it</strong>: craigmbrown.com/api/v2/ (Streamable HTTP MCP)<br>\n                            <strong>Docs</strong>: github.com/craigmbrown/blindoracle-docs</p>\n\n                            <p class=\"post-hashtags\">#MCP #AgentTrust #NostrProofs #BlindOracle #x402 #AgentIdentity</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- ============================================ -->",
